
    README for Perl distribution Lingua-PT-Stemmer

This distribution provides stemmers for Portuguese and Galician.

    Lingua::PT::Stemmer
    Lingua::GL::Stemmer

You can read a nicely formatted version of the documentation for
the modules online:

    https://metacpan.org/pod/Lingua::PT::Stemmer
    https://metacpan.org/pod/Lingua::GL::Stemmer

You should be able to install this using your usual method for installing
modules from CPAN. If you don't have one, have a look at:

    http://www.cpan.org/modules/INSTALL.html

This module was written by Xern <xern@cpan.org>

